T02TD2735AE:114a-0: @114a * // spyan ras gzigs dbang mgon po mchog la bstod pa yin /
T02TD2735AE:114a-1: bsod nams gang zhing zla ba dung ltar dkar ba des//
T02TD2735AE:114b-0: @114b rgyal ba kun gyi sras kyi thu bo de lta bur //
T02TD2735AE:114b-1: sdug bsngal 'gro la mi 'jigs stsol ba nyid gyur cig / ral pa 'chang zhing shin tu zhi ba yangs pa'i spyan //
T02TD2735AE:114b-2: rtag par rab tu dang bzla ba'i dkyil 'khor zhal //
T02TD2735AE:114b-3: lha dang lha min rnams kyis zhabs kyi 'dam skyes la //
T02TD2735AE:114b-4: phyag byas nor bu padma las byung mgon por 'dud //
T02TD2735AE:114b-6: klu'i rgyal po nor rgyas kyi bus bstod pa /
T02TD2735AE:114b-7: dpal nags kyi rin chen gyi zhal sngar bsod nams rnam par rgyal bas bsgyur ba'o//
